reset-token.disclaimer-text:
Dear Valuable customer, please follow these steps to reactivate your Soft Token:

  1. Delete the Soft Token using below steps  
    1. Please access Al-Rajhi Business Token
    2. Select the Soft Token serial number “<Token serial Number >”
    3. Click on manage icon, system will open list of options
    4. Click on option “Delete eCorporate Token”
    5. Click on “Ok”
    6. The token will be removed from your list

 

  1. Add Soft Token:
    1. Please click on “Proceed” button, accordingly Al-Rajhi bank will send SMS includes (Activation Code & Activation Password)
    2. Please access Al-Rajhi Business Token
    3. Click on the icon “Add New Token”
    4. Enter Activation code & Activation Password
    5. Click on “Ok”
    6. The token will be added to token’s list
